title: Play thousands of old-school arcade games on your PC.
description:
"Extra M.A.M.E." - a small MS Windows compatible GUI wrapper for M.A.M.E., the Multiple Arcade Machine Emulator authored by Nicola Salmoria and the MAME team. M.A.M.E. let&#039;s you play thousands of old-school arcade games on your computer. "Extra M.A.M.E." is smaller and easier to use. It doesn&#039;t force you to fuss with difficult configurations and it&#039;s compatible with all M.A.M.E games.

System requirements: 
     OS Windows 95/98/Me/NT/2k/2k3/XP
     Minimum screen resolution 800x600 
     Pentium processor and above 
     16 Mb RAM 
     5 Mb free disk space

Latest news: http://www.godlikedevelopers.com/
